
03/01/2020
Acronyms :
S3 - Simple Storage Service
ec2 - Elastic Compute
vpc- Virtual Private Cloud
rds - relation database service
iam - identity and access management


1.) IAM - identity and access management -
Enables us to manage or access AWS services securely
We can create users groups and use permissions to allow or deny their access to AWS resources

Common Features
1.) Manage Users and their Access
2) Manager Access for Federated Users
3.) Services with no additional charge
4.) Fine grain access to AWS resources

